{
  "stem": "19195.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 334.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was an incident once that I witnessed that a man came over, and he took one of the little girls on his lap.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he kissed this kid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was about four years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the teacher came over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she says, can-- can we take Martha away, because she has to go to sleep?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She's very tired.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then a couple of days later, I noticed that this-- the teacher was drilling this kid.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Martha, who was that man?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She started crying, and she shook her [? hands. ?] She says, don't talk to me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm very sad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Finally, they calmed her down, and she stopped crying.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But she also had a brother there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were two of them-- Robi, and her name was Martha.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there were about, I would say, about 100 kids, all for the same reason, that orphanage.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] she said, Martha, who-- who was that man?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Tell me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I won't tell anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she started crying and crying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "All of the sudden, she said, that's my mother's husband.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we-- the teachers trained those children not to reveal, because we had to-- and they were coming, the officials, to check what kind of an orphanage.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were like, say, about 500 feet from a munition factory there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And those sirens were terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The kids were scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We also-- We also had [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] downstairs-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was, when the kids, you know, couldn't go out and play, so they would play down in that-- I forgot how you call.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And those kids somehow, I'll never forget, and I never did forget.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
